                     <interp inst="t18311201-275-person2079" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was at work in the garden where the cloak was thrown; I took it up and gave it to Fry.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I have always got my living in an honest way, and hope this will be a warning to me.</p>
